{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act44side", "eventName": "墟", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "AT-7", "avgTag": "行動前", "storyName": "冷月", "storyInfo": "花火大會、繼位儀式……一切開始之前，更紗為三船送上了一份大禮——她駭進金石台的訊號，向整座城市播出北院入侵的緊急警報，使得三船焦頭爛額。以此為契機，所有人都開始了各自的行動。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "64_g14_mifuneoffice", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$loading_intro", "key": "$loading_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$fireworks", "volume": 0.5}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "從電視台的頂樓俯瞰，夜空中煙火零星升起，又緩緩下墜，一直落到腳下不可見的地方。"}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "花火大會尚未正式開始，這不過是大會開始前的熱身活動。"}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "斐迪亞凝視著玻璃反射中的自己，和自己身後重鑄後的般若。"}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1896_1#4$1", "duration": 1.0, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……般若。", "name": "三船"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1896_1#4$1"}, {"id": 17, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "二十年過去，你終於到了我的手裡……可惜，太遲了。", "name": "三船"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1896_1#4$1"}, {"id": 18, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "除了代替鐵齋，被打扮成這次儀式的承認者以外，你又能為我做些什麼呢？", "name": "三船"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1896_1#4$1"}, {"id": 19, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "斐迪亞仔細端詳著重鑄後的般若，忽然注意到內側把手上明顯黏著膠痕，大概是被什麼綁帶纏了很長時間。"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1896_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "內側沒動過，是嗎？", "name": "三船"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1896_1#4$1"}, {"id": 23, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1896_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……真是面好盾，但也就這樣了。", "name": "三船"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1896_1#4$1"}, {"id": 25, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1896_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "澪！", "name": "三船"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1896_1#4$1"}, {"id": 27, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clog_fts", "volume": 1.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "c"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "c", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1901_1#1$1", "posfrom": "200,0", "posto": "50,0", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1896_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "距離典禮正式開始還有多久？", "name": "三船"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1896_1#1$1"}, {"id": 34, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1901_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一個小時左右。", "name": "澪"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1901_1#1$1"}, {"id": 36, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1896_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好。我下樓透透氣。", "name": "三船"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1896_1#1$1"}, {"id": 38, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1901_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "三船先生，星熊很有可能突襲會場。", "name": "澪"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1901_1#5$1"}, {"id": 40, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1896_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我正等著她來呢。", "name": "三船"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1896_1#9$1"}, {"id": 42, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1901_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您的意思是？", "name": "澪"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1901_1#1$1"}, {"id": 44, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1896_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她來到這裡無非出現兩種情況——要嘛已經被逼瘋，要嘛竟然還能在鐵齋死後保持冷靜。", "name": "三船"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1896_1#9$1"}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但不管她是什麼樣子，在我的地盤上，在我的鏡頭下，電視上的她，也不過是個瘋狂的殺人鬼。", "name": "三船"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1896_1#9$1"}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "到時候，這個瘋女人就只會是這次繼位儀式的註腳，陷入瘋狂的失敗者。就算我敵不過她，也會有上面的人來幫我收拾她的。", "name": "三船"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1896_1#9$1"}, {"id": 48, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1901_1#3$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "萌萌香她……", "name": "澪"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1901_1#3$1"}, {"id": 50, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1896_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不忍心了？", "name": "三船"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1896_1#9$1"}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也罷，那就再留一陣子吧，把她徹底榨乾。我們有的是手段讓她就範——", "name": "三船"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1896_1#9$1"}, {"id": 53, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1896_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等等，這樣也得留那個叫吉星的一條命，免得徹底讓萌萌香絕望。你還沒處理掉她吧？", "name": "三船"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1896_1#1$1"}, {"id": 55, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1901_1#3$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒有。", "name": "澪"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1901_1#3$1"}, {"id": 57, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1896_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那就好。", "name": "三船"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1896_1#9$1"}, {"id": 59, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對了，哲也呢？", "name": "三船"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1896_1#9$1"}, {"id": 60, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1901_1#3$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "澪"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1901_1#3$1"}, {"id": 62, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1896_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "澪？", "name": "三船"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1896_1#1$1"}, {"id": 64, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1901_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……我沒能看住他。", "name": "澪"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1901_1#2$1"}, {"id": 66, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1896_1#7$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你？沒能看住他？", "name": "三船"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1896_1#7$1"}, {"id": 68, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "三船的聲音突然變得陰沉狠毒。"}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1896_1#6$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說實話。", "name": "三船"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1896_1#6$1"}, {"id": 72, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1901_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……我把他放走了。", "name": "澪"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1901_1#2$1"}, {"id": 74, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1896_1#6$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還是惻隱之心？", "name": "三船"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1896_1#6$1"}, {"id": 76, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1901_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是。", "name": "澪"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1901_1#2$1"}, {"id": 78, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1896_1#6$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "僅此而已？", "name": "三船"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1896_1#6$1"}, {"id": 80, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1901_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "僅此而已。", "name": "澪"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1901_1#5$1"}, {"id": 82, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1896_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我對你很失望。", "name": "三船"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1896_1#2$1"}, {"id": 84, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1901_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "願受懲罰。", "name": "澪"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1901_1#5$1"}, {"id": 86, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1896_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "算了。現在正是用人之際，我先不跟你計較。不過，該換一下你的任務了。", "name": "三船"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1896_1#1$1"}, {"id": 88, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "假如星熊真的打過來了，你去對付她。", "name": "三船"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1896_1#1$1"}, {"id": 89, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1901_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是我分內之事。", "name": "澪"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1901_1#5$1"}, {"id": 91, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1896_1#6$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別急著答應。", "name": "三船"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1896_1#6$1"}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果她活著走到了我面前，你應該知道自己的下場是什麼。", "name": "三船"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1896_1#6$1"}, {"id": 94, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1901_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "澪"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1901_1#5$1"}, {"id": 96, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1901_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……是。", "name": "澪"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1901_1#2$1"}, {"id": 98, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1896_1#6$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "從現在開始，隨時都會有兩名忍者盯著你。別想耍什麼花招。", "name": "三船"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1896_1#6$1"}, {"id": 100, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我出去透透氣。告訴所有人，做好應對所有突發情況的準備。", "name": "三船"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1896_1#6$1"}, {"id": 101, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "64_g2_jindastreet_n", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_firework_amb", "volume": 0.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "f"}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.3, "channel": "f", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.2, "channel": "f", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1909_1#1$1", "posfrom": "300,0", "posto": "0,0", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1912_1#1$1", "posfrom": "200,0", "posto": "-50,0", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1909_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "花火大會還有一下才開始，現在只是暖身活動。我們繼續在這邊逛一下吧。", "name": "欣喜的路人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1909_1#1$1"}, {"id": 120, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1912_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不好吧，親愛的，我們就應該直接去河對面的花火大會會場。城際網路上好多人在說，這片區域現在不安全。", "name": "冷靜的路人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1912_1#1$1"}, {"id": 122, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有小道消息說金石會的會長死了。怪談中的那個青鬼砍死了他。", "name": "冷靜的路人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1912_1#1$1"}, {"id": 123, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1909_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "欸——是那個傳媒大亨，金什麼的嗎？", "name": "欣喜的路人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1909_1#1$1"}, {"id": 125, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1912_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不是不是，那個是三船。死掉的是鐵齋。", "name": "冷靜的路人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1912_1#1$1"}, {"id": 127, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1909_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "欸——我看平常都是三船出現，還以為是他死了呢。", "name": "欣喜的路人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1909_1#1$1"}, {"id": 129, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1912_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "鍛冶町那邊好像也有一些不好的消息，加上最近一直在傳的北院間諜……總之，還是先去河對岸吧。", "name": "冷靜的路人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1912_1#1$1"}, {"id": 131, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "posfrom": "-50,0", "posto": "-200,0", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "-200,0", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1896_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.2, "channel": "f", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "cg_firework", "screenadapt": "coverall", "xScale": 1.05, "yScale": 1.05, "fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"xScaleFrom": 1.05, "yScaleFrom": 1.05, "xScaleTo": 1.0, "yScaleTo": 1.0, "duration": 20.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_firework_huge", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怪談。帶風向。操弄輿論。"}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這一套流程，他已經熟悉到不能再熟悉了。"}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "誰又猜得到，御機所有怪談的來源，不過是島須拿議員候選人的事威脅自己，又死在自己刀下呢？"}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "島須的死需要掩蓋，剛起步的電視台需要話題，剛剛攀上關係的議員正等著看自己處事的手腕。"}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "於是自己狠下心，把星熊和新安芸市那個“沉默的佐原”混合起來，將所謂兇宅當成一整週的熱門話題報導，結果一炮而紅。"}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "高強度的拍攝打消了看熱鬧的民眾的疑心，又為自己留下了充足的善後和誤導空間。"}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怪談帶來的熱度變成錢，錢打動了議員，禁錮了警察，讓金石會對自己唯命是從，連鐵齋也無從置喙。"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在那之後，一切都一發不可收拾。兇宅成了絕佳的處理礙事之人的場所。"}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但這樣的把戲不可能永遠持續下去。興趣會消退，收益會減少，與日俱增的，只會是鐵齋的懷疑和輿論的壓力。"}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "於是，在最後一個知道議員候選人死因的組員被處理掉後，自己開始拓寬“怪談”的範圍和管道。"}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "神明可以是怪談，事故可以是怪談，哪怕無事發生，只要有人願意講一個引人入勝又讓人脊背發涼的故事，那也可以是怪談。"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "自己曾經也疑惑過，御機的居民們，何以對怪談趨之若鶩呢？"}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們懼怕生活中任何可能的危險，卻又難以壓抑好奇的視線，彷彿那點危險對他們有著致命的吸引力。"}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "無論如何，電視台為金石會提供了源源不斷的收入，反過來又拉動了晶體元件產業，讓自己成了鐵齋看不上，卻又離不開的人。"}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而那時的鐵齋對自己來說，已經只是一個……"}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "f", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.1}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.1, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$alarmenter", "volume": 0.8}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.3, "r": 1.0, "g": 0.2, "b": 0.2, "fadetime": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$alarmenter", "volume": 0.8}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.3, "r": 1.0, "g": 0.2, "b": 0.2, "fadetime": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……？！", "name": "三船"}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "緊急通知……", "name": "電視裡的聲音"}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$m_bat_imprisonment_intro", "key": "$m_bat_imprisonment_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.1, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "64_i07", "screenadapt": "coverall", "xScale": 1.05, "yScale": 1.05, "fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"xScaleFrom": 1.05, "yScaleFrom": 1.05, "xScaleTo": 1.0, "yScaleTo": 1.0, "duration": 20.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {"name": "$eb_064cg_alart", "layer": 1.0}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.1}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_oldtvelectricity", "volume": 1.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "o"}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "緊急通知，緊急通知。", "x": 300.0, "y": 350.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "這不是演習，這不是演習。", "x": 300.0, "y": 350.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼回事？地震？！", "name": "慌張的路人"}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "御機目前正遭到北院軍隊的全面攻擊，御機目前正遭到北院軍隊的全面攻擊。", "x": 300.0, "y": 350.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "為了您的人身安全，請遵守以下指示：", "x": 300.0, "y": 350.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "北院軍隊入侵？怎麼可能？！", "name": "驚懼的路人"}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "請身處室內的民眾立刻關閉門窗，關閉室內燈光，等待下一步指示。", "x": 300.0, "y": 350.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 720.0}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "請身處室外的民眾前往距離您最近的避難設施，就近避難。", "x": 300.0, "y": 350.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "避、避難設施？御機有這種東西嗎？", "name": "無措的路人"}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "以前好像有宣傳過，現在、現在只能看著街道上的路牌慢慢找了……", "name": "呼吸急促的路人"}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不僅僅是仁田街，整個御機的夜晚，除了對地面上的事情一無所知的煙火，忽然被密密麻麻的紅光攪亂。"}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那是正在被遺忘的恐懼。"}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "血峰戰役之後，南北之間的衝突不減反增，但呼嘯著發展的經濟實在太過震耳欲聾，以至於人們對邊境傳來的炮火聲越來越充耳不聞。"}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "即便到九十年代之後，無論御機還是鎖川，都未放棄將對面作為假想敵的預案，但雙方的民眾卻已徹底將這種可能拋到腦後。"}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "終於，被遺忘多年卻無人能置身事外的恐懼在御機民眾心中湧現，那是任何怪談都比不上的、難以言狀的無措感。"}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "三船先生！", "name": "焦急的忍者"}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "到底發生什麼事情了？！", "name": "三船"}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有人駭進了金石台的廣播網，在政府發給我們備用的緊急影像上動了手腳，還……還向全御機放了出來！", "name": "焦急的忍者"}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那個人甚至利用我們難以辨別的技術手段間接控制了一部分其他電視台的廣播網，好幾家合作廠商也受到了影響。", "name": "焦急的忍者"}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "合作廠商以為這是我們的官方行為，差點就把我們的電話打爆了！", "name": "焦急的忍者"}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_transmissionget", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喂？現在究竟是什麼情況——", "name": "三船"}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "議員大人？！", "name": "三船"}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "o", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "64_g17_jindaalley_n", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$transmission", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1044_hsgma2_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "森內，你那邊的潛入行動還順利嗎？", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_1044_hsgma2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 244, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好得很，人群全亂了，電視台裡的人進進出出，我很容易就混進去了。", "name": "森內"}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1044_hsgma2_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "更紗，稍微適可而止一點。這樣的假消息可能會引發意想不到的後果。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_1044_hsgma2_1#5$1"}, {"id": 248, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "放心，我特地避開了花火大會之類人擠人的區域，還有醫院、學校、養老院這種人們心臟承受能力都不太好的地方。", "name": "更紗"}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而且警報播放幾遍之後，就會播放一個聲稱剛剛只是誤播的澄清影片啦。", "name": "更紗"}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我先帶著萌萌香和吉星過去繼位儀式的會場了。", "name": "更紗"}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "星熊，鬧出下一個大風波的任務，就交給你了。", "name": "更紗"}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1044_hsgma2_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "瞭解。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_1044_hsgma2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 255, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_highheelfts", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "64_g2_jindastreet_n", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_crwddiscuss_outside", "volume": 0.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "cr"}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.6, "channel": "cr", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "cr", "fadetime": 10.0}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "星熊一路逆著混亂的人群，走向電視台。"}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "正如更紗所說，大多數電視都開始播放所謂的“澄清影片”，而驚魂未定的人群也漸漸冷靜下來。"}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "趕路的途中，她其實想過，會不會從人群身上看到自己期待的反應。"}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不必是什麼如夢初醒，或者居安思危一類沉重又討人厭的東西。"}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她只想看見寒顫。一個切切實實地回想起恐懼為何物，而不是將其貶為幸福生活中的一點調劑的寒顫。"}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但她只聽見許多人興高采烈地重複著一個詞……"}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“怪談”。"}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$faceoff_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_highheelfts", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1044_hsgma2_1#2$1", "posfrom": "200,0", "posto": "0,0", "duration": 2.0, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……到了。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_1044_hsgma2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 281, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看來電視台真的是亂成一團了，門口的警戒也太鬆了吧？", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_1044_hsgma2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 282, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "獨角的鬼毫無躊躇地往樓內走去。她經過一個，兩個，三個工作人員，沒人注意到她。"}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "直到第四個人……"}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1908_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "青鬼？！", "name": "眼尖的工作人員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1908_1#1$1"}, {"id": 287, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "青鬼！快叫金石會的人！", "name": "眼尖的工作人員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1908_1#1$1"}, {"id": 289, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothmovement", "volume": 0.5}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1916_1#1$1", "posfrom": "200,20", "posto": "0,0", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.2}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothmovementsp", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1917_1#1$1", "posfrom": "-200,20", "posto": "0,0", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.8}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral", "volume": 1.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "r"}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "r", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1044_hsgma2_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "各位還是給我讓開一條路，這樣比較穩妥。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1916_1#1$1"}, {"id": 304, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1916_1#1$1", "posfrom": "50,0", "posto": "50,0", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 1.0, "duration": 0.0}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1917_1#1$1", "posfrom": "-50,0", "posto": "-50,0", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 1.0, "duration": 0.0}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 1.0, "duration": 0.0, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "黑道和忍者們"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1916_1#1$1"}, {"id": 309, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1044_hsgma2_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不走？", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1916_1#1$1"}, {"id": 312, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "儘管星熊被黑道和忍者重重包圍，但在圍著她的這些人心中，不知為何，一股懼意始終縈繞不去，反而就像……"}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不是他們包圍了她，而是她一個人包圍了在場的所有人。"}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1044_hsgma2_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果哪位聽說過二十年前，“金石會的青鬼”在御機做過什麼，就該知道，我是為了你們好。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1916_1#1$1"}, {"id": 317, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哪怕各位和我已經不是手足，哪怕你們的老大……害死了鐵齋叔，我仍然不想和你們交手。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1916_1#1$1"}, {"id": 318, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1044_hsgma2_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "走吧，讓我去見金兵衛。別逼我。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1916_1#1$1"}, {"id": 320, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1907_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別、別以為你逃得掉！", "name": "心虛的黑道"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1916_1#1$1"}, {"id": 322, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "金石會從來沒發過將你“破門”或者“絕緣”的公告，你現在仍然是金石會的一員！對我們動手，就是對自己的家人動手！", "name": "心虛的黑道"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1916_1#1$1"}, {"id": 323, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1044_hsgma2_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……這種話你們自己會信嗎？", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1916_1#1$1"}, {"id": 325, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "無人應答。"}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "星熊若無其事地朝著樓內走去。"}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_bldwhoosh", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_metalcollar", "volume": 0.5}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她的身後沒有腳步聲，只傳來了什麼細小的東西破空的聲音。"}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她沒去看那到底是什麼。無論那個東西是匕首，是隨身碟，是手裏劍，甚至只是一把豆子，此時都已經不再重要。"}}, {"id": 335, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1044_hsgma2_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "匕首上的力道不足啊，會讓人覺得你不是在丟暗器，而是在撒豆驅鬼。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_1044_hsgma2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 337, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "鬼出去，福進來，對吧？", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_1044_hsgma2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 338, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你要是能老老實實就範，我們的確可以撒點豆子了事。我們之間沒有仇。", "name": "為首的黑道"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}, {"id": 340, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1044_hsgma2_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒有仇？也許吧，不過在我那個時候，鍛冶町撒豆子的規矩是反過來的。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_1044_hsgma2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 342, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們當年喊的是，福出去……", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_1044_hsgma2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 343, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1044_hsgma2_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "鬼進門。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_1044_hsgma2_1#7$1"}, {"id": 345, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_drawsword", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 349, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她拔刀出鞘。"}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "曾聽聞青鬼惡名的黑道們不由自主地向後退去，唯有一個看起來還算年輕的黑道上前一步，打算出這個極有可能要命的風頭。"}}, {"id": 351, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1044_hsgma2_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 352, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……很好。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_1044_hsgma2_1#7$1"}, {"id": 353, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothmovement", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 355, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "action": "zoom", "poszoom": "0.5,0.5", "scale": 1.05, "duration": 0.2}}, {"id": 356, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 0.2}}, {"id": 357, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 358, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 359, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 360, "prop": "background", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 361, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.1, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 362, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_firemagic", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 363, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_tswordlight", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 364, "prop": "Effect", "attributes": {"name": "$e_hoshiguma_slash", "rox": 0.0, "roy": 0.0, "roz": 180.0, "layer": 1.0}}, {"id": 365, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 366, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 367, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.1, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 368, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "64_g2_jindastreet_n", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 369, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 370, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 15.0, "ystrength": 15.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 371, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$bodyfalldown2", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 372, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 373, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒人看清獨角的鬼究竟做了什麼。他們只看見青色的光芒閃過，年輕黑道腿上多了一道鮮血淋漓的傷口，撲通一聲摔倒在地。"}}, {"id": 374, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 375, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別……別怕！兄弟們上！", "name": "為首的黑道"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}, {"id": 376, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們是……我們是橫行天下的金石會，都給我抬頭挺胸，給我上！不能丟金石會、丟三船會長的臉！", "name": "為首的黑道"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1906_1#1$1"}, {"id": 377, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 378, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_drawsword", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 379, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 380, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 381, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 382, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 383, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 3.0, "xstrength": 10.0, "ystrength": 10.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 384, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_soldiersrun", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 385, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_audience_chaos", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 386, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 387, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 388, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1044_hsgma2_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 389, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這才像話嘛。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_1044_hsgma2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 390, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 391, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "於是，人群如潮水般朝獨自向前邁步的鬼進發。"}}, {"id": 392, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而鬼只是一步又一步地向前走去，直到離面前的人近得不能再近——"}}, {"id": 393, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "青色的火光再次亮起，這次，所有人都看清了，那不再壓抑憤怒的鬼的真正身姿。"}}, {"id": 394, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 395, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_churchfire", "volume": 1.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "b"}}, {"id": 396, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "b", "fadetime": 6.0}}, {"id": 397, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.2, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 398, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.2, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 399, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 400, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 20.0, "ystrength": 20.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 401, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.03, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 402, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 403, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$swordtsing4", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 404, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 405, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 406, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 20.0, "ystrength": 20.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 407, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.03, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 408, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$swordtsing3", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 409, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g":